Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:51.67,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}就算死也要一直做你的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:56.05,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}但是真心哭泣的你怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:59.14,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}决不让你心寒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.97,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}和我擦干眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:04.60,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}没有圣剑也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.56,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}不是勇者也没关系
